prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and humorous dreamy fantasy art style greeting card front. The scene is a magical beach where the sand is made of sparkling rainbow glitter and the ocean has gentle, glowing pastel waves of pink, lavender, and turquoise. In the center of the scene, cartoon-illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are comically attempting to build an elaborate, wobbly sandcastle that defies gravity. Jordan, in his tan hoodie, is precariously placing a seashell on the very top turret, looking very focused and slightly nervous. Lao Lao, in her blue sweatshirt, is laughing joyfully as she holds a giant, oversized clam shell full of glowing magical water, about to pour it into the sandcastle's moat. Surrounding them, silly-looking crabs with tiny birthday party hats scuttle by, carrying miniature birthday presents and slices of cake. The sky is a dreamy twilight with a soft, ethereal glow, filled with floating, iridescent bubbles instead of clouds. In the center of the composition, written in a beautiful, looping handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!". The overall vibe is playful, magical, and full of lighthearted fun. Flat 2D artwork for printing.
